nodes.text: Star Wars Collector Edition 2013: The Prequel Trilogy

Star Wars Collector Edition 2013: The Prequel Trilogy was a book released on August 1, 2012 in the United Kingdom by Pedigree Books Limited. It featured the stories and in-depth profiles of the Prequel trilogy.

The book mistakenly states that Anakin Skywalker was born on Tatooine, and that Grievious was a droid. Boles Roor is also misidentified as Bos Roar. It also states that Darth Maul was killed in the lightsaber fight on Naboo.
